					<![CDATA[
						 <p>This is so uncomfortably weebish and borderline stereotypical at points that it was painful to read.</p> <p>Also,</p> <blockquote> <p>These sacs are also found within the vaginal cavity.</p> </blockquote> <p>I fail to see why this is a detail necessary for the article.</p> <p>-1</p> 
