					<item>
				<guid>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13473152#post-4705333</guid>
				<title>Site crit OS</title>
				<link>http://www.scpwiki.com/forum/t-13473152/scp-5507#post-4705333</link>
				<description></description>
				<pubDate>Tue, 30 Jun 2020 20:55:49 +0000</pubDate>
				<wikidot:authorName>ManyMeats</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>2104082</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>The video logs parse as a bit difficult for me to read. I am the type of person who &quot;says&quot; the articles out loud in my head while I read, so symbols and foreign languages slow me down and compromise my enjoyment.</p> <p>Having said that, the body horror here is <em>thorough</em> and considerate. Some of the language around the various objects could maybe do with a bit of tightening up but it's not like it's a problem, just an area for possible refinement. Overall, this seems in tune with what I know of and expect from a neo-sarkic jam and liked the rampant body horror enough to give this a safe +1.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
